reset_parasitics(25.10)                                reset_parasitics(25.10)

Name
       reset_parasitics

Syntax
       reset_parasitics

       [-help]

       Deletes  the  parasitic database without resetting the extraction modes
       specified using the setExtractRCMode command.

Parameter
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the reset_parasitics parameter.

